{"id":"mizzah","term":"Mizzah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Despair, one of the four sons of Reuel, the son of Esau (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:13\">Gen. 36:13</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:17\">17</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:13","Genesis 36:17"]}